"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the line segments that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"connect them. For example, you could use an polyline to represent a road or the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path along which something moves."}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/BlockingGesturesExample":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/blockinggesturesexample","kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Constrain the map to a certain area."}],"title":"Blocking Gestures","role":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/BlockingGesturesExample","type":"topic"}}}